{"word":"ἐναντίος","slug":"ἐναντίος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐναντίος, α, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀντί\">ἀντί</a></el> via <el>ἀντίος</el> ‘set against’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘in facing position’, <b>facing:</b> of wind <b><a href='B:470 14:24'>Mt 14:24</a>; <a href='B:480 6:48'>Mk 6:48</a>; <a href='B:510 27:4'>Ac 27:4</a>;</b> of a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξ\">ἐξ</a> ἐναντίας</el> <b><a href='B:480 15:39'>Mk 15:39</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘in opposition’, <b><a href='B:590 2:15'>1 Th 2:15</a></b> (hostile); <el>ἐναντῖα πράσσειν <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρός\">πρός</a></el> engage in opposition to <b><a href='B:510 26:9'>Ac 26:9</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐναντίον\">ἐναντίον</a> τῷ λαῷ</el> contrary to the interests of the people <b><a href='B:510 28:17'>28:17</a>;</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξ\">ἐξ</a> ἐ.</el> the contrary one <b><a href='B:630 2:8'>Tit 2:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐναντίον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐναργής\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}